    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$35,500 - Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for, offering a smooth, reliable ride and a very clean interior. It\u2019s a wonderful choice for anyone looking for a high-quality, dependable car that still looks great and performs beautifully!",
